  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI market research pipeline with competitor analysis and white-space detection",
    "Feature deep research with multi-competitor implementation analysis",
    "Recursive build graphs that break features into implementable tasks",
    "AgentForge: agentic coding automation that creates GitHub PRs autonomously",
    "Competitive signal intelligence with real-time company monitoring",
    "AI chat agent with access to 1000+ integrations via Composio",
    "One-tap export to Linear, Jira, Slack, Notion, and GitHub",
    "Event-driven automations triggered by research, builds, and signals",
    "Real-time streaming via NDJSON and multiplexed WebSocket",
    "Daily rolling credit system with per-user fair scheduling"
